            <scopecontent>
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                                 <p>Leather goods, agricultural and practical implements, and livestock are the main categories of goods included in this account book of a store, the location of which is perhaps Bloomington, Ill. The accounts are for customers, most of whom lived in Illinois, Indiana, Michigan, and Wisconsin.</p>
